  "detailed_description": "VITATIO 3 brings a new take on the precision game genre, traverse your physics based ship through the asteroid belt in this infinite running score based avoidance game, upgrade your ship, unlock new paint jobs and customize your cockpit<br />\r\n<br />\r\n★ DIFFICULT GAMEPLAY!<br />\r\nThere are 3 standard modes, easy, medium and hard plus an unlockable mode DAFT which is where end game players compete for bragging rights<br />\r\n<br />\r\n★ TRAIN YOUR REFLEXES!<br />\r\nVITATIO 3 is a game that favours the strong minded, it will test your patience and every time you lose, you are becoming better!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n★ ACHIEVEMENTS!<br />\r\nOver 90 achievements for you to unlock!",
  "about_the_game": "VITATIO 3 brings a new take on the precision game genre, traverse your physics based ship through the asteroid belt in this infinite running score based avoidance game, upgrade your ship, unlock new paint jobs and customize your cockpit<br />\r\n<br />\r\n★ DIFFICULT GAMEPLAY!<br />\r\nThere are 3 standard modes, easy, medium and hard plus an unlockable mode DAFT which is where end game players compete for bragging rights<br />\r\n<br />\r\n★ TRAIN YOUR REFLEXES!<br />\r\nVITATIO 3 is a game that favours the strong minded, it will test your patience and every time you lose, you are becoming better!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n★ ACHIEVEMENTS!<br />\r\nOver 90 achievements for you to unlock!",
